701954f.title: Bronx: Valentine Avenue - Bedford Park Boulevard
701954f.text:
Valentine Avenue, west side, north from but not including
Bedford Park Boulevard to E. 201st Street.
May 6, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
701954f.folder: Valentine Avenue & Bedford Park Boulevard, Bronx, NY

701952f-a.title: Bronx: Valentine Avenue - Bedford Park Boulevard
701952f-a.text:
Valentine Avenue, west side, south from Bedford Park Boulevard
to E. 199th Street. The frame house, at the S.W. corner of the two
thoroughfares has stood here since about 1893 and bears No. 216 Bedford
Park Boulevard. The 6-story building bears No. 2927-2931 Valentine Avenue.
May 5, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
